><p>饰演美泰高管格洛丽亚的亚美莉卡·费雷拉透露，最关键的对话序列之一——关于女性面临的双重标准—— <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/america-ferrera-reveals-barbie-monologue-scene-took-up-to-50-takes-3473011">拍摄了 30 到 50 次</a>。</p><p> “它在页面上起作用了，所以我绝对想给表演它的观众带来这种感觉——让它像我读到页面上的文字时那样与我产生共鸣，”费雷拉告诉<em><a href="https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2023/07/america-ferrera-barbie-monologue-30-to-50-times?utm_brand=vf&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_social-type=owned&amp;mbid=social_facebook" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《名利场》</a></em> 。</p><p>这位演员表示，虽然“感觉像是”拍摄了 500 场，但实际上可能接近 30 到 50 场“完整镜头”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3467452" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3467452" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3467452" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/barbie-2000x1270-1.jpg" alt="《芭比娃娃》中的安娜·克鲁兹·凯恩、莎朗·鲁尼、亚历山德拉·希普、玛格特·罗比、哈里·内夫和艾玛·麦基" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/barbie-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/barbie-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/barbie-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/barbie-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/barbie-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/barbie-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3467452" class="wp-caption-text"> （LR）Ana Cruz Kayne、Sharon Rooney、Alexandra Shipp、Margot Robbie、Hari Nef 和 Emma Mackey 均在《芭比娃娃》（2013 年）中饰演芭比娃娃。图片来源：华纳兄弟影业</figcaption></figure><p>在其他<em>芭比</em>新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/barbies-marketing-budget-was-more-than-it-cost-to-make-the-film-3472627">最近有消息称营销预算超过了电影的制作成本</a>。</p><p>据<em><a href="https://variety.com/2023/film/box-office/barbie-marketing-campaign-explained-warner-bros-1235677922/" target="_bla